Comment: 1,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}OP FRAME 1 — TL
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}OP FRAME 1 — TL II
Comment: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:52.09,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The scenery's pretty invigorating, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.67,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yunosagi's over there.
Comment: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.84,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll be able to take some great pictures here.
Comment: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hello, Isami speaking.
Comment: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.56,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, hey...
Comment: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,They've just opened up,
Comment: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've already got so many customers, eh?
Comment: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.82,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,I've now heard everyone's opinions.
Comment: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.16,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,Any other thoughts?
Comment: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:31.46,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to hear what the younger\N generation expects from a hot spring inn.
Comment: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.09,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.21,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Who was the one who said we\N only had to sit here and do nothing?
Comment: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.51,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Give us your honest opinions please.
Comment: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.76,Default,Woman2,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Comment: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Comment: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:48.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I think it ought to be full of food\N you want to eat yet be cheap as well.
Comment: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.10,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Such as?
Comment: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:54.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A cheap all-you-can-eat buffet that serves meat
Comment: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and cake from morning to evening!
Comment: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh, and maybe a luxurious coach,
Comment: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which is comfortable enough to\N sleep in, that drops you off at Yunosagi!
Comment: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:06.49,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,O-oh, I think an indoor pool that uses\N water from the hot spring would be nice.
Comment: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.54,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yup! A pool is an absolute necessity!
Comment: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.63,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,There may be guests that want to swim at all hours.
Comment: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.09,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yup, I bet!
Comment: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:17.38,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It would be awesome if the\N coaches served cake on board too!
Comment: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.22,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Right, everything's prepared!
Comment: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.97,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Then, let's present this to\N Madam Manager, young master!
Comment: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.14,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Young master!
Comment: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.47,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Comment: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.48,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,How's the inn supposed to run when its\N own young master lacks self-confidence?
Comment: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.19,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,An important factor in giving a convincing presentation
Comment: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.53,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,is that the presenter themselves are motivated!
Comment: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.74,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Comment: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.20,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll understand how much we respect
Comment: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kissui Inn after she hears our plans.
Comment: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.87,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Now come on. Let's go!
Comment: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.87,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Comment: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But you know, this inn is really great!
Comment: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.42,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Really, you think so?
Comment: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Tomoe?
Comment: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:12.10,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Kissui Inn will only need to\N invest a tenth of the production cost.
Comment: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:15.40,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! It'll work like magic—
Comment: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.82,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,The benefits gained from the advertising will be huge.
Comment: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:22.61,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,The masses of people who watch the movie will all want to stay at this inn at least once,
Comment: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.24,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,and as a consequence, they'll all visit Yunosagi.
Comment: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.78,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Of course, none of this is guaranteed.
Comment: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.08,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,But from my experience, I—
Comment: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:34.50,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Please allow me to speak\N with the young master in private.
Comment: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.75,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.46,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Mind if I join the conversation?
Comment: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.97,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd like Takako to join our conversation.
Comment: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:43.51,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Comment: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.43,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Fine, I get it.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:54.06,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'll leave you to have this conversation in private.
Comment: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.27,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What? Uhh...
Comment: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What have you got planned, Nakochi?
Comment: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.36,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm going to the beach with my brothers.
Comment: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.69,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What about you, Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.70,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll be working here the whole summer.
Comment: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.28,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Oh! Then let's go to the beach together!
Comment: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.24,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,The beach is great!
Comment: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.83,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd love to meet your brothers!
Comment: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.46,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness! You've got to hear this!
Comment: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.79,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,It's a movie! A movie!
Comment: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Comment: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.67,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Comment: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.63,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,They're filming a movie at Kissui Inn!
Comment: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.30,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.60,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh, what should I do?
Comment: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.97,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I need to go home and tell my family!
Comment: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:32.93,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.52,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I wonder what part I'm going to be playing.
Comment: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A movie?
Comment: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.90,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Yeah. At Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.61,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Wow!
Comment: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.83,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,So...
Comment: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.00,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You understand, right?
Comment: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's not just our problem.
Comment: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.18,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,At this rate, the whole of Yunosagi\N will gradually become poorer and poorer.
Comment: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:14.18,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I was shocked when Takako asked\N whether we wanted to be filmed or not, but—
Comment: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.64,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I have no objections.
Comment: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.27,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.27,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'll allow you free reign to do what you want this time.
Comment: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.86,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.45,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Anyway, due to a\N strongly-worded request from the director,
Comment: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.53,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,we're thinking about offering you roles in the film,
Comment: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,even if they're big ones.
Comment: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:38.16,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'd like to hold a small\N audition when the director comes.
Comment: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.62,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Comment: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's going to be an amazing summer!
Comment: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:49.22,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'd like to play a great female spy who's an ex-Olympic high diver!
Comment: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:50.55,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Bang!
Comment: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Hey, Minchi, what kind of role do you want?
Comment: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I want—
Comment: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.76,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,A chef.
Comment: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But we're acting in a movie!
Comment: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be whatever you want!
Comment: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:04.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A female police officer, a cabin attendant, a nurse—
Comment: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.98,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you a perverted old man?
Comment: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.74,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,As expected from Minchi...
Comment: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.91,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:19.54,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,I heard you've left the young master in\N charge of the investment for the movie.
Comment: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.04,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Comment: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.34,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,A movie... how wonderful.
Comment: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:28.84,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Mariko Kaga from {\i1}Withered Flower{\i0\fscx160} {\r}was very cute.
Comment: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.05,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Oh, so you still aren't withered, are you, Denroku?
Comment: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.39,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Not yet, I'm afraid.
Comment: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:41.94,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,I'm asking you because you're dedicated enough to relocate to the countryside in order to write.
Comment: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.07,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,You want me to write 40 pages\N to take up 10 minutes of the film?
Comment: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:51.74,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Please write us a scene that\N shows the real warmth of this area.
Comment: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:55.49,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,When do I get the chance to talk to the\N director and the main writer about this?
Comment: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:59.37,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll give you an outline of the basic setting and plot.
Comment: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you mind writing\N something as a springboard for discussion?
Comment: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.46,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,After that, I'll take and talk to the director about it.
Comment: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.59,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.17,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:13.84,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,I've heard that there's this event called a\N "Bonbori Festival" that takes place around here.
Comment: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.05,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,How about getting a description of that? Okay?
Comment: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:20.31,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Mr. Jiromaru, the young master specifically requested that they
Comment: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,include your writing in the film\N as a condition of the investment.
Comment: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.06,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Comment: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.15,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Comment: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:36.49,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,They'll be checking the actual\N operational portions of the inn.
Comment: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.33,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What I need you all to do is brush up everything.
Comment: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,This... is a pool?
Comment: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.33,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I heard that it used to be one.
Comment: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.08,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.25,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Basically, you want us to clean this, right?
Comment: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.26,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,The pool must be used in the film as well.
Comment: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.22,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,In other words,
Comment: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's another condition imposed by\N the young master for the investment.
Comment: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:59.47,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Do you have anything to say, young master?
Comment: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:04.48,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,This place is scheduled to be an\N important stage for the upcoming film,
Comment: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.94,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,so please ensure that it's left sparkling.
Comment: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But why the pool in particular?
Comment: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.23,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.94,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's a summer film!
Comment: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.45,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Summer means the pool!
Comment: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The pool means summer!
Comment: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.49,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,And... I wasn't wrong.
Comment: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.03,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Anyway, please take care of it.
Comment: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.79,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Party... Party...
Comment: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.33,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Addicted to parties!
Comment: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.54,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Young master!
Comment: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:13.17,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I don't even know how to begin to thank you.
Comment: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.21,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,You've given me such a great chance—
Comment: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:20.05,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Those who work hard will be\N granted an opportunity as a reward.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.22,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Comment: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.76,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.56,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We've both worked so hard up until now.
Comment: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.48,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.23,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It was a hard life.
Comment: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.44,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Looking back, there were\N times we struggled shamelessly...
Comment: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.36,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Helplessly flailing around...
Comment: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.44,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.11,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,But that's all over now.
Comment: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.57,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,This small yet absolute flame in our hearts
Comment: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:43.45,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,tells us that what we've been doing hasn't been in vain.
Comment: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.66,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Okay...
Comment: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.79,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Comment: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:51.25,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh, we're also going to be\N taking half of the manuscript fee
Comment: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:55.00,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,and the royalties as payment for the\N room you've been staying in for free.
Comment: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.05,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Just keep that in mind.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.09,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Comment: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:06.85,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll give you a call sometime during\N the week, and drop by again with the director.
Comment: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.81,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Director Matsumura will be visiting?!
Comment: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.94,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,His first work, {\i1}Wet Button{\i0}, was incredible!
Comment: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.23,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Oh, we'll also be bringing the two leads for the movie.
Comment: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.98,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,{\an8}His second—
Comment: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.19,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,They'd like to see the inn it\N takes place in as soon as they can.
Comment: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.99,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.78,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,We'd like to sign the contract then as well.
Comment: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.24,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting.
Comment: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.62,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting!
Comment: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.45,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Madam Manager will be here shortly.
Comment: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.08,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Please come in—
Comment: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.71,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,We'll wait here.
Comment: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.71,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.33,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Can I be of assistance in her place?
Comment: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.01,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Please, come this way.
Comment: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:29.56,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,We'd like to lend you a hand in this brilliant idea of yours.
Comment: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:33.44,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,The film will be a bigger success if you\N make the entirety of Yunosagi its stage.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.94,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Comment: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Since business is pretty bad these days, we can split the
Comment: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,cost of the investment between all of\N the inns. Wouldn't that help Kissui Inn?
Comment: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.40,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly!
Comment: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.65,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Comment: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.53,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Comment: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.58,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I appreciate your offer to help,
Comment: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.70,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,but the location of the filming\N will be limited solely to Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.71,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We don't plan on changing that.
Comment: 0,0:12:54.71,0:13:00.09,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Oh, then why are we paying to advertise Kissui Inn?
Comment: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.72,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Which is why I've been saying that you don't need to pay.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.55,Default,All,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.77,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana, you've got to concentrate!
Comment: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:24.53,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,I wonder when he turned into such a fine young master.
Comment: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:28.32,Default,Woman2,0,0,0,,It's amazing how he's planned to do everything on his own.
Comment: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:35.29,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Either way, Kissui Inn is\N responsible for whatever happens.
Comment: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:49.22,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I hear he firmly rejected the offer from the other inns.
Comment: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.39,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.52,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,The young master sure has changed.
Comment: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:56.39,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,It's like he's more confident in himself now.
Comment: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.73,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I guess men really do change after doing something big.
Comment: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.73,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,A movie, eh... That's a giant bet.
Comment: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.49,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,So, what role are you playing, Mr. Ren?
Comment: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.45,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Mr. Ren is in it too?!
Comment: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:13.58,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,The director wants people\N working at the inn to be in the movie.
Comment: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.70,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Wow...
Comment: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.50,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Comment: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Maybe.
Comment: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.83,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Your hands have stopped moving, Tohru.
Comment: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.34,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.50,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Okay, guess I had better head back to work.
Comment: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.26,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm going to peel the white radish.
Comment: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:33.01,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Now that Tomoe mentioned it, Tohru's also excited...
Comment: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.27,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Why is everyone so hyped?
Comment: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a chef going to do in a movie anyway?
Comment: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.02,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,But I get the feeling that\N Tohru would look good on screen...
Comment: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.78,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Oops.
Comment: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.15,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Alright!
Comment: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Alright!
Comment: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.66,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Alright!
Comment: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.49,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Wow! Awesome!
Comment: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.16,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's a crane!
Comment: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.25,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah, a movie's gotta have a crane!
Comment: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.75,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,This is Ms. Suehiro, the lead actress of the film.
Comment: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.26,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Comment: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Actresses are so different from\N ordinary people, aren't they, Nakochi?
Comment: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.34,Default,Suehiro,0,0,0,,{\a6}I look forward to working with you all.
Comment: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:21.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That day, they started doing the test shoots...
Comment: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I-I'm so nervous!
Comment: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.91,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Calm down, Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.08,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I've brought some cold tea.
Comment: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.29,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. Please come in.
Comment: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.35,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,This is so good!
Comment: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.77,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.90,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,This is a wonderful inn.
Comment: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.44,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,I really like it here.
Comment: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:11.57,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'd like to make a personal visit here sometime.
Comment: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.86,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kind words.
Comment: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.66,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It's quite an old building.
Comment: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's hard to keep everything down.
Comment: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:25.13,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Yes, it was already 60 years old\N when it was passed down to me.
Comment: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.38,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Wow, 60 years?!
Comment: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:32.51,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,After such a long time, seams\N come apart in places that can't be seen.
Comment: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.88,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.76,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Oh, Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.52,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Ms. Suehiro, I was wondering if you could give us an autograph
Comment: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,which we could use to decorate the hallway.
Comment: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.35,Default,Sue,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.82,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I was surprised to hear that Madam\N Manager agreed to the filming in the first place!
Comment: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.07,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard she gave her consent right away.
Comment: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Maybe she really wanted a role in the movie.
Comment: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.87,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Maybe!
Comment: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.71,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take the main character's place for now?!
Comment: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.80,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,It's just for the camera test.
Comment: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.92,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Comment: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.05,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,The main character's running late.
Comment: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.30,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Think of it as an additional benefit!
Comment: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.10,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,You can walk arm-in-arm with Ms. Suehiro.
Comment: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A just married couple!
Comment: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.98,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Wow, that's incredible!
Comment: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.19,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Show us what you've got, young master!
Comment: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.19,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.07,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.24,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako, I'm ready.
Comment: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.62,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.91,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Okay, get a little closer!
Comment: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.29,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,The director insisted on\N someone more muscular for the role.
Comment: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.50,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\a6}There! Perfect!
Comment: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\a6}Very nice!
Comment: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.83,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.09,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Come on, stop playing around!
Comment: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.60,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Minchi! Hurry up!
Comment: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.74,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm so tired!
Comment: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.91,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Let's take a short break...
Comment: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.03,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.16,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let's take a break, Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm so tired...
Comment: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.84,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Me too, but we've gotten this place pretty clean.
Comment: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.22,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a lot better than it was before.
Comment: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.51,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,We've only got a bit more to do.
Comment: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah, only a—
Comment: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What? What?!
Comment: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.31,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.57,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm very thankful to you, Takako.
Comment: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.78,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's a movie.
Comment: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.70,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I definitely wouldn't have been able to do this myself.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.60,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Comment: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.85,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom?
Comment: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.60,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Comment: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.27,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Comment: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:48.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Do you remember when we went to the\N presentation for the movie the Film Club made?
Comment: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.29,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:52.79,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,During college, the fall of your first year.
Comment: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.38,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Nope, not really.
Comment: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.46,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.17,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember it?
Comment: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:05.14,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Oh, that perverted film that only consisted of\N clips of a middle school girl in a school swimsuit.
Comment: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.97,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,In this day and age, that\N director would be sent straight to jail.
Comment: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.31,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,That was my first piece of work as a writer.
Comment: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.14,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.23,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,First and last, though.
Comment: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:21.57,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We were originally going to make a\N longer version of it at the Film Club,
Comment: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.86,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,but the guy who was supposed to direct it quit.
Comment: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:28.28,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,That made all the other members lose interest too.
Comment: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.37,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.41,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah, so I decided to film it myself.
Comment: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.33,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,How should I put it...
Comment: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.96,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Something I experienced in my youth...
Comment: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My identity...
Comment: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.26,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Are those girls doing their job?
Comment: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:48.39,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,My sister is definitely more suited to running Kissui Inn than I am.
Comment: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.64,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:53.14,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Both my mother and I thought that.
Comment: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.10,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Shijima...
Comment: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.36,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You haven't called me by that name since college!
Comment: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.28,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.83,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'll get some tea.
Comment: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.00,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Your sister's name is Satsuki, right?
Comment: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.63,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,She's really quick-minded.
Comment: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.84,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,She always talks in a precise, clipped style.
Comment: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I think she's got charisma.
Comment: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.22,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,She was really popular at school...
Comment: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.10,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,She looked so bright in my eyes.
Comment: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.68,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Beautiful, intelligent...
Comment: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.52,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It was as though she was living in a different world.
Comment: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:38.15,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,A creature completely unrelated to me.
Comment: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.18,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,You didn't agree to that, did you?
Comment: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.68,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Don't say something so rash.
Comment: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.35,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I'm finished! The manuscript is complete!
Comment: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.89,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We won't be finished like this! You hear me?!
Comment: 1,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.39,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We shall return!
Comment: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{}{\a6}Yunosagi Cirrus
Comment: 100,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.62,Dialogue,Nako,0,0,0,,{}Eh?
Comment: 100,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.20,Dialogue,Enishi,0,0,0,,{}Eh?
Comment: 100,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.66,Dialogue,Ohana,0,0,0,,{}Oh?
